<br>
Because that disc that boosts your defensive performance gives you the best defensive, thus making counters balanced according to it, thus making it required.<br>
<br>
But that disc that boosts your offensive performance does not give you the best offense and is rarely used due to the necessity of #1 and because of these 2 things it makes it more of a fun disc than a required disc.  And as warriors we are constantly told that our only point is to absorb damage, thus that makes anything outside of that humdrum norm naturally more fun and exciting than it really is.<br>
